{"text_id":55727,"tokens":["How"," to"," Deal"," With"," a"," Dep","ressed"," Person","\n","Caring"," for"," a"," person"," with"," depression"," can"," be"," a"," difficult"," task","."," The"," person"," may"," not"," always"," be"," open"," to"," discussing"," their"," feelings",","," leaving"," you"," uncertain"," of"," how"," best"," to"," support"," them","."," Knowing"," the"," signs"," of"," depression"," and"," managing"," your"," own"," personal"," needs"," while"," supporting"," the"," person"," through"," their"," difficult"," journey"," can"," be"," an"," important"," part"," of"," providing"," care","."," ","\n\n","Learning"," About"," Depression","\n","It","'","s"," important"," to"," understand"," the"," signs"," of"," depression"," so"," that"," you"," can"," recognize"," them"," when"," they"," occur","."," Common"," symptoms"," of"," depression"," in"," adults"," can"," include"," persistent"," feelings"," of"," sadness",","," hopelessness",","," and"," lethargy",";"," irritability",";"," loss"," of"," interest"," in"," activities"," that"," once"," provided"," enjoyment",";"," changes"," in"," sleeping"," and"," eating"," habits",";"," difficulty"," concentrating",";"," persistent"," physical"," symptoms"," that"," don","'","t"," respond"," to"," treatment",";"," thoughts"," of"," death"," or"," suicide",";"," and"," trouble"," functioning"," at"," work"," or"," home","."," ","\n\n","Tuning"," in"," to"," Their"," Status","\n","When"," attempting"," to"," care"," for"," someone"," with"," depression",","," it","'","s"," important"," to"," be"," aware"," of"," how"," they","'","re"," feeling","."," If"," they","'","re"," not"," willing"," to"," talk",","," be"," an"," attentive"," listener","."," Pay"," attention"," to"," how"," they"," interact"," with"," people",","," the"," activities"," they"," take"," part"," in",","," the"," conversations"," you"," have",","," and"," the"," topics"," discussed","."," Notice"," changes"," in"," appetite",","," how"," they"," sleep",","," and"," their"," energy"," levels","."," With"," this"," information"," in"," hand",","," you"," can"," make"," more"," accurate"," observations"," and"," assumptions"," about"," what"," your"," friend"," may"," be"," going"," through","."," ","\n\n","Become"," Aware"," of"," What"," Helps"," and"," What"," Doesn","'","t","\n","Everyone"," is"," different",","," so"," pay"," close"," attention"," to"," what"," works"," and"," what"," doesn","'","t"," when"," trying"," to"," help"," the"," depressed"," person","."," Different"," activities",","," tasks",","," and"," conversations"," may"," mean"," different"," things"," to"," them","."," Offer"," different"," approaches"," and"," see"," what"," helps"," them"," the"," most"," in"," terms"," of"," feeling"," better","."," ","\n\n","Tell"," Them"," You"," Care","\n","Letting"," the"," person"," know"," that"," you"," care"," about"," them"," and"," are"," willing"," to"," do"," whatever"," you"," can"," to"," help"," is"," a"," great"," place"," to"," start","."," A"," simple"," \u201c","I"," love"," you"," and"," am"," here"," for"," you","\u201d"," or"," \u201c","How"," can"," I"," support"," you","?\u201d"," can"," go"," a"," long"," way","."," ","\n\n","Listen"," Deep","ly"," ","\n","In"," addition"," to"," offering"," your"," support",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," really"," listen","."," Make"," sure"," that"," the"," person"," knows"," you"," are"," listening"," by"," not"," stepping"," in"," and"," cutting"," them"," off"," when"," they"," start"," to"," talk","."," Show"," that"," you","'","re"," paying"," attention"," with"," body"," language"," and"," facial"," expressions","."," Express"," understanding"," and"," encourage"," them"," to"," continue"," talking","."," ","\n\n","Accept"," St","ated"," Feelings"," ","\n","Anyone"," struggling"," with"," depression"," has"," likely"," experienced"," feelings"," of"," guilt"," and"," maybe"," even"," shame"," about"," their"," condition","."," Resist"," the"," temptation"," to"," try"," and"," talk"," them"," out"," of"," feeling"," down"," and"," instead",","," encourage"," them"," to"," talk"," about"," these"," feelings","."," Let"," them"," know"," that"," it","'","s"," okay"," to"," feel"," what"," they"," do"," and"," help"," them"," find"," ways"," to"," express"," these"," emotions"," produ","ctively","."," ","\n\n","Stay"," Connected"," Remote","ly"," ","\n","For"," some"," people",","," the"," idea"," of"," having"," to"," talk"," about"," their"," feelings"," is"," just"," too"," overwhelming",","," and"," this"," is"," where"," staying"," connected"," remotely"," can"," be"," helpful","."," This"," may"," include"," sending"," texts",","," messages",","," or"," emails","."," It","'","s"," important"," to"," start"," out"," with"," small"," conversations"," and"," gradually"," build"," up"," to"," more"," in","-","depth"," conversations"," about"," their"," feelings","."," ","\n\n","Plan"," to"," Meet"," in"," Person"," ","\n","It","'","s"," important"," to"," make"," plans"," to"," meet"," with"," the"," depressed"," person"," in"," person","."," While"," it","'","s"," great"," to"," stay"," connected"," remotely",","," it"," can"," be"," much"," more"," beneficial"," to"," meet"," in"," person"," and"," really"," be"," there"," for"," the"," person","."," Set"," up"," a"," specific"," date"," and"," time"," to"," meet"," and"," let"," them"," know"," that"," you","'","re"," looking"," forward"," to"," seeing"," them","."," ","\n\n","Up"," the"," Activity"," Level","\n","When"," someone"," is"," depressed",","," it"," can"," be"," hard"," to"," motivate"," yourself"," to"," actually"," do"," something","."," Suggest"," activities"," that"," you"," can"," do"," together"," such"," as"," taking"," a"," walk",","," or"," doing"," some"," yoga",","," or"," just"," chatting"," in"," a"," cafe","."," A"," change"," of"," scenery"," can"," be"," a"," great"," way"," to"," shake"," off"," the"," blues"," and"," occupying"," the"," mind"," with"," something"," else"," can"," be"," incredibly"," helpful","."," ","\n\n","Do"," Cho","res"," as"," a"," Team","\n","Often"," times"," when"," someone"," is"," dealing"," with"," depression",","," mundane"," tasks"," such"," as"," cleaning"," and"," doing"," laundry"," can"," become"," too"," overwhelming"," to"," handle","."," Ask"," if"," there"," is"," anything"," you"," can"," do"," to"," help",","," for"," example"," offer"," to"," go"," shopping"," or"," do"," the"," laundry"," together","."," It","'","s"," important"," to"," remember"," that"," this"," is"," not"," solely"," the"," person","'","s"," responsibility"," to"," take"," care"," of","."," ","\n\n","Focus"," On"," Self","-","Care"," Together","\n","Self","-","care"," is"," an"," essential"," part"," of"," dealing"," with"," depression","."," Encourage"," your"," friend"," to"," find"," ways"," to"," nourish"," the"," mind",","," body",","," and"," spirit","."," This"," could"," include"," something"," as"," simple"," as"," writing"," in"," a"," journal",","," or"," going"," for"," a"," walk",","," or"," doing"," a"," creative"," project","."," Show"," them"," that"," you"," are"," there"," to"," support"," them"," throughout"," the"," process","."," ","\n\n","Initi","ate"," a"," Conversation"," About"," Outside"," Help","\n","It","'","s"," important"," to"," recognize"," when"," a"," person"," needs"," outside"," help","."," Opening"," a"," conversation"," about"," therapy"," or"," a"," support"," group"," is"," a"," great"," way"," to"," get"," the"," person"," a"," step"," closer"," to"," feeling"," better","."," Be"," sure"," to"," offer"," your"," support"," throughout"," and"," let"," them"," know"," that"," it","'","s"," okay"," to"," take"," this"," step","."," ","\n\n","Learn"," About"," Different"," Options"," Together","\n","Some"," people"," may"," find"," it"," easier"," to"," talk"," about"," what"," type"," of"," help"," they"